OL,3,CI feel sick: Little-Pengelly breaks
OL,4,Csilence on Donaldson 'danger' claim
OL,6,FEmma Little-Pengelly has broken her
OL,7,Fsilence to deny knowing anything about
OL,8,FJeffrey Donaldson's wrongdoing.
OL,10,FShe said claims from one woman that
OL,11,Fshe once described the disgraced
OL,12,Fpaedophile as a "danger," were not her
OL,13,Fwords.
OL,15,FIn an interview with UTV, the deputy
OL,16,FFirst Minister said she "absolutely"
OL,17,Fdid not see any inappropriate
OL,18,Fbehaviour by the former DUP leader.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
