OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1783880423
OL,3,CI feel sick: Little-Pengelly breaks
OL,4,Csilence on Donaldson 'danger' claim
OL,6,F"I feel really sick even saying his
OL,7,Fname because of that betrayal," Emma
OL,8,FLittle-Pengelly said.
OL,10,FWatch Tracey Magee's interview with
OL,11,FEmma Little-Pengelly in full.
OL,13,FShe said that the image the public saw
OL,14,Fof Donaldson was the same she saw
OL,15,Fbehind the scenes.
OL,17,F"I saw nothing that was a cause for
OL,18,Fconcern," she told UTV.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
