OL,3,CI feel sick: Little-Pengelly breaks
OL,4,Csilence on Donaldson 'danger' claim
OL,6,FLast month Donaldson was convicted at
OL,7,FNewry Crown Court of 18 sex offences,
OL,8,Fincluding one count of rape, relating
OL,9,Fto abuse of two women when they were
OL,10,Fchildren.
OL,12,FMs Little-Pengelly said she is "deeply
OL,13,Fsickened and repulsed by what has come
OL,14,Fout".
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
