PN,41904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1783880423
OL,3,CI feel sick: Little-Pengelly breaks
OL,4,Csilence on Donaldson 'danger' claim
OL,6,FShe said: "I did not know that this
OL,7,Fman was a sexual predator. I did not
OL,8,Fknow that this man was a predator
OL,9,Ftowards children. It is absolutely
OL,10,Fagainst every value that I would have
OL,11,Fif I'd known that and would not have
OL,12,Fgone to the police, would not have
OL,13,Fimmediately severed all and any
OL,14,Fcontact with this person."
OL,16,FEmma Little-Pengelly was co-opted to
OL,17,FDonaldson's MLA chair in Lagan Valley
OL,18,Fand was appointed by him as deputy
OL,19,FFirst Minster.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
