PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1783880423
OL,3,CI feel sick: Little-Pengelly breaks
OL,4,Csilence on Donaldson 'danger' claim
OL,6,FShe said there was nothing over the 20-
OL,7,Fyear period she knew the politician
OL,8,Fwhich hinted at his double life.
OL,10,F"Up until his arrest, I didn't see
OL,11,Fanything that I would have given me
OL,12,Fany rise for concern in terms of him
OL,13,Fbeing a sexual offender, of him being
OL,14,Fa paedophile," Ms Little-Pengelly said.
OL,16,F"I was not told anything by anybody
OL,17,Fthat would have given me any sense of
OL,18,Fthat whatsoever. So this has been
OL,19,Fabsolutely shocking."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/15
