OL,3,CI feel sick: Little-Pengelly breaks
OL,4,Csilence on Donaldson 'danger' claim
OL,6,FEarlier this week, the Belfast
OL,7,FTelegraph reported that a young girl
OL,8,Fthat Ian Paisley had previously
OL,9,Fdescribed in a text exchange was a
OL,10,Fvictim of Donaldson's. He was not
OL,11,Freferring to the two victims of
OL,12,FDonaldson's sex abuse trial.
OL,14,FThe news organisation reported that
OL,15,FEmma Little-Pengelly told her that
OL,16,FJeffrey Donaldson was a "danger" to
OL,17,Fher.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
