PN,41907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1783880423
OL,3,CI feel sick: Little-Pengelly breaks
OL,4,Csilence on Donaldson 'danger' claim
OL,6,FEmma Little-Pengelly said: "I have
OL,7,Flooked back over that period of time.
OL,8,FI cannot be clearer. Look, I can't
OL,9,Fspeak for this woman. I can't explain
OL,10,Fwhat she was thinking whenever she
OL,11,Fsaid that.
OL,13,F"These are not my words but what I can
OL,14,Fsay absolutely clearly... absolutely
OL,15,Fclearly is I seen absolutely nothing.
OL,17,F"I witnessed nothing at that time that
OL,18,Fgave me any cause of concern. I was
OL,19,Fnot told anything about Jeffrey
OL,20,FDonaldson that gave me any cause of
OL,21,Fconcern.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
