PN,41908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1783880423
OL,3,CI feel sick: Little-Pengelly breaks
OL,4,Csilence on Donaldson 'danger' claim
OL,6,F"So in 2020, I did not believe that
OL,7,FJeffrey Donaldson was a danger to
OL,8,Fanyone. And if I had thought that he
OL,9,Fwas a danger to anyone, not only would
OL,10,FI have told people, but I would not
OL,11,Fhave been friendly with Jeffrey
OL,12,FDonaldson."
OL,14,FThe Northern Ireland Assembly has
OL,15,Fbegun a review into alleged abuse or
OL,16,Finappropriate behaviour associated
OL,17,Fwith Jeffrey Donaldson in Stormont.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
