PN,41909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1783880423
OL,3,CI feel sick: Little-Pengelly breaks
OL,4,Csilence on Donaldson 'danger' claim
OL,6,FFormer DUP leader Donaldson was last
OL,7,Fmonth convicted at Newry Crown Court
OL,8,Fof 18 sex offences, including one
OL,9,Fcount of rape, relating to abuse of
OL,10,Ftwo women when they were children.
OL,12,FOn June 29, Assembly Speaker Edwin
OL,13,FPoots asked the clerk and chief
OL,14,Fexecutive of the Assembly to conduct a
OL,15,Freview into any allegations of "any
OL,16,Fabuse or inappropriate behaviour by
OL,17,FJeffrey Donaldson" at Parliament
OL,18,FBuildings in Belfast.
OL,26,@wD@`OUyD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,420,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1783880423
OL,3,CI feel sick: Little-Pengelly breaks
OL,4,Csilence on Donaldson 'danger' claim
OL,6,FThe Assembly announced on Friday that
OL,7,Fit had put in place arrangements to
OL,8,Fconduct the review.
OL,10,FIt will be conducted by the director
OL,11,Fof parliamentary services (senior
OL,12,FAssembly safeguarding officer), guided
OL,13,Fby experts in trauma-informed
OL,14,Fpractices, and report directly to the
OL,15,Fclerk and chief executive.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,420,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1783880423
OL,3,CI feel sick: Little-Pengelly breaks
OL,4,Csilence on Donaldson 'danger' claim
OL,6,FThe review will allow any member or
OL,7,Fformer member, as well as staff and
OL,8,Fother users of the Parliament
OL,9,FBuildings, to bring forward any
OL,10,Fincidents of abuse they directly
OL,11,Fexperienced.
OL,13,FIt is to establish if the Assembly
OL,14,FCommission holds any information about
OL,15,Fabuse or inappropriate behaviour while
OL,16,FDonaldson was a member of the Assembly
OL,17,Ffrom 2003 to 2010, or while he was a
OL,18,Fvisitor to Parliament Buildings as an
OL,19,FMP.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
