PN,41912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1783880423
OL,3,CI feel sick: Little-Pengelly breaks
OL,4,Csilence on Donaldson 'danger' claim
OL,6,FIt will be carried out from July 10
OL,7,Funtil August 21, with a report due by
OL,8,FAugust 28.
OL,10,FThe review is also designed to draw
OL,11,Fthe clerk's attention to any matters
OL,12,Fthat "may require further appropriate
OL,13,Finvestigation or referral to the PSNI
OL,14,For other statutory agencies".
OL,16,FEarlier, it was confirmed that
OL,17,FDonaldson has been removed from the
OL,18,FPrivy Council, a body of senior
OL,19,Fadvisers to the King.
OL,26,@tD@FOUvD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
