CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1783880423
OL,3,CI feel sick: Little-Pengelly breaks
OL,4,Csilence on Donaldson 'danger' claim
OL,6,FIn a statement from the clerk of the
OL,7,FPrivy Council, it was confirmed that
OL,8,FDonaldson had asked for his name to be
OL,9,Fremoved from the list of members last
OL,10,Fmonth.
OL,12,FThe clerk said: "Now, therefore, by
OL,13,Fand with the advice of His Majesty's
OL,14,FPrivy Council, it is hereby ordered
OL,15,Fthat the name of the said Jeffrey
OL,16,FDonaldson be removed from the list of
OL,17,FMembers of His Majesty's Most
OL,18,FHonourable Privy Council."
OL,26,@tD@QOUzD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
